      "raw_text": "The Yakima valley will be irrigat-\ned. Secretary Hitchcock yesterday\napproved the Tieton irrigation pro-\nject and set aside out of the re-\nclamation fund $1,750,000 which is\nto become Immediately available\nfor the work which will commence\nas soon as the department can get\nout the specifications. Representa-\ntive Jones and Senator Ankeny\nwere particularly active in secur-\ning this concession."
    }
